<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="fix-vt">fix <strong><em>vt</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /fɪks/    美 /fɪks/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>使固定；安装；牢记：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>fix a mirror on the wall 
在墙上装镜子</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He fixed in his mind all the wonders of that particular day.
他牢记着在那个特别的日子里发生的所有奇迹。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-set-fix-up">2.★ <strong>确定；决定 (set)；安排 (fix up)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They have <strong>fixed a date</strong> for the meeting.
他们已经确定了开会的日期。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>fix a trip
安排一次旅行</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>修理；整理；解决 (问题)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Before the trip, I'd had my car fixed.
出发前，我找人修理了我的汽车。</p></div>

<p>注: fix更常用来指修理机器、车辆等，没有repair 正式。  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Let me just fix my hair before we go out.
让我整理下头发再出门。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>In my memory he could fix any problem.
在我的记忆中，他能解决任何问题。</p><footer>2011重庆</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="fix-on-upon">fix … on / upon</h3>
<p>1.<strong>集中 (目光、注意力等) 于：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>fixed my eyes on</strong> the word “congratulations.”
我的眼睛盯着“祝贺你”这几个字。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You must <strong>fix your attention on</strong> what the teacher is saying.
你必须集中注意力听老师讲。</p></div>

<h3 id="fix-up">fix up</h3>
<p>1.<strong>修理好；安顿；安排：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They fixed up the house before they moved in.
他们把房子修整好才搬进去。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They fixed me up for the night in a hotel.
他们安排我在一家旅馆过夜。</p></div></div>